Package: vkchat
Type: Package
Title: Easy communication with OpenAI API to enable chat-based applications
Version: 0.0.5
Authors@R: person("Rodrigo", "Serrano", , "roserrano@vikua.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Wrappers to facilitate use of OpenAI API, currently two approach are developed: 
    `Insights` to enable knowledge creation based on specific dataframes
    `Idiomatic` chat-with-your-data type of application.
